01:02:01,923 --> 01:02:03,174
Aku tahu siapa kau.

760
01:02:05,468 --> 01:02:06,427
Kau Eun-u, 'kan?

761
01:02:07,011 --> 01:02:08,554
Bagaimana bisa tahu?

